      "updated": 1771601356965,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "req (fn & non fn)\ncore entities (data model/schemas)\nAPI\nhigh lvl design => fn\ndeep dives => non fn",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "req (fn & non fn)\ncore entities (data model/schemas)\nAPI\nhigh lvl design => fn\ndeep dives => non fn",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "mWtNjVTyRPtKdnI4Jm2Zd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 442.42578125,
      "y": 230.46484375,
      "width": 812.059326171875,
      "height": 825,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b7O",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1927055264,
      "version": 1144,
      "versionNonce": 769267296,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771637035625,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "store all msgs? => yes\nhow long do we want to store => all time\nmedia/ audio? => yes\nhow big are our media/ audio? => 1MB\ndo we want to see the person being online? status\n\n50 million DAU\nhow many concurrent messages? whats the freq to expect?\nhow big is each message? => (~100Bytes) no capped at 100kB\nwhat percentage of them contains media/ audio?\n\ndo we support group messages? => yes\nhow big is each group? => 100ppl? yes\n\n\nFUNC:\n- we want to have create groups\n- send/ receive messages between ppl within the chat groups\n- send/ receive AVs\n- status of user\n\n---OOS----\nAV calling, nearby friends etc.\nedit group members?\n\nNON-FUNC:\n- low latency in terms of receiving messages(<500ms)\n- ensure message is definitely received (consistency in terms of receiving messages)\n- billions of users, high throughput\n- all msgs stored\n- Availability >> consistency\n---OOS----\nmultiple devices for single client, crazy big groups",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "store all msgs? => yes\nhow long do we want to store => all time\nmedia/ audio? => yes\nhow big are our media/ audio? => 1MB\ndo we want to see the person being online? status\n\n50 million DAU\nhow many concurrent messages? whats the freq to expect?\nhow big is each message? => (~100Bytes) no capped at 100kB\nwhat percentage of them contains media/ audio?\n\ndo we support group messages? => yes\nhow big is each group? => 100ppl? yes\n\n\nFUNC:\n- we want to have create groups\n- send/ receive messages between ppl within the chat groups\n- send/ receive AVs\n- status of user\n\n---OOS----\nAV calling, nearby friends etc.\nedit group members?\n\nNON-FUNC:\n- low latency in terms of receiving messages(<500ms)\n- ensure message is definitely received (consistency in terms of receiving messages)\n- billions of users, high throughput\n- all msgs stored\n- Availability >> consistency\n---OOS----\nmultiple devices for single client, crazy big groups",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
