      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771637154796,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "API\nwhich protocol should we use?\n    real time updates deep dive -> various options for clients & servers connectivity\nchoose web socket => no need peer to peer distribution\n*RESTFul API doesnt make as much sense\nSimple polling, long polling, SSE(server side events), web sockets\n\nCOMMANDS SENT\ncreateChat\nsendMessage\nreceiveMessage\nsendStatus\nreceiveStatuses",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API\nwhich protocol should we use?\n    real time updates deep dive -> various options for clients & servers connectivity\nchoose web socket => no need peer to peer distribution\n*RESTFul API doesnt make as much sense\nSimple polling, long polling, SSE(server side events), web sockets\n\nCOMMANDS SENT\ncreateChat\nsendMessage\nreceiveMessage\nsendStatus\nreceiveStatuses",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
