      "text": "1. find all groups for user\n2. find users in a group chat\n\nChat\n    chatId\n    name\n    created_at\n    metadata....\n\nChatParticipant => Composite\n    participantId (FK)\n    chatId\n\nMessage\n    messageId\n    content\n    senderId\n    chatId\n\nInbox\n    participantId\n    messageId\n\nUser\n    userId\n    name\n    profilePic\n    metadata...",
